Package: dafishr
Title: Download, Wrangle, and Analyse VMS data
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Fabio", "Favoretto", email = "fabio@gocmarineprogram.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6493-4254")),
           person("Eduardo", "Leon Solorzano", email = "leonsol.eduardo@gmail.com", role = c("ctb"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6493-4254")))
Description: The package allows to download, clean and analyse raw VMS data from Mexican government. You can use the vms_download function to download raw data, or you can use the sample_dataset provided 
    within the package. You can follow the tutorial in the vignette available at https://cbmc-gcmp.github.io/dafishr/index.html. 
